No. 471,

Misc.

Sinks v. United States. Richard J. Flynn for petitioner. Solicitor General Cox, Assistant Attorney General Miller, Beatrice Rosenberg and Julia P. Cooper for the United States.

Motion to strike supplemental record and portions of memorandum of United States relating thereto denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit denied.
